    <string name="token_info_intro_body">wBKC is the wrapped version of BrokerChain\'s native token, BKC. It is pegged 1:1 to BKC. Deposit BKC to receive wBKC, and unwrap wBKC to get the same amount of BKC back. Do not send funds to the contract address. Use your wallet address to receive wBKC.</string>
